@startuml
title Authentication Flow (Based on Actual AuthenticationService)

actor User
participant "React Native App" as App
participant "AuthController" as Controller
participant "AuthenticationService" as Service
participant "UserRepository" as Repository
participant "MySQL (Users)" as DB
participant "JWT Generator (Nimbus)" as JWT
participant "AsyncStorage" as Storage

autonumber

== Login Request ==

User -> App: Enter username & password
App -> Controller: POST /identity/api/auth/login
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: authenticate(request)
activate Service


== User Lookup ==

Service -> Repository: findByUsername(username)
activate Repository
Repository -> DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE username=?
activate DB
DB -->> Repository: User entity
deactivate DB
Repository -->> Service: Optional<User>
deactivate Repository

alt User not found
    Service -> Controller: Throw USER_DID_NOT_EXIST
    Controller -->> App: 401 Unauthorized
    deactivate Service
    deactivate Controller
else User exists

    Service -> Service: BCryptPasswordEncoder.matches()

    alt Password incorrect
        Service -> Controller: Throw UNAUTHENTICATED
        Controller -->> App: 401 Unauthorized
        deactivate Service
        deactivate Controller
    else Password correct

        == JWT Creation ==

        Service -> JWT: Build JWTClaimsSet
        note right
        Claims:
        - sub = username
        - iss = IOT.com
        - iat = now
        - exp = now + 1 hour
        - scope = roles + permissions
        end note

        Service -> JWT: Sign with HS512 (SECRET_KEY)
        JWT -->> Service: Serialized token

        Service -->> Controller: AuthenticationResponse{token}
        deactivate Service

        Controller -->> App: 200 OK {token}
        deactivate Controller

    end
end


== Token Storage ==

App -> Storage: setItem('@jwt_token', token)
Storage -->> App: OK

App -> App: Mark authenticated = true
App -> App: Navigate to HomeScreen


== Using Token in Requests ==

App -> Controller: GET /api/devices
note right
Authorization: Bearer <JWT>
end note

@enduml
